OL,3,CFamilies 'trying to survive instead of
OL,4,Cthrive' amid childcare crisis
OL,6,FPressure is mounting on the Northern
OL,7,FIreland Executive to provide urgent
OL,8,Ffinancial intervention, as childcare
OL,9,Fproviders warn the sector is on the
OL,10,Fbrink of collapse.
OL,12,FDespite the new education minister
OL,13,Fprioritising childcare in his first
OL,14,Fspeech, Northern Ireland is the only
OL,15,Fpart of the UK without a strategy and,
OL,16,Faccording to campaigners, reinvests
OL,17,Fzero percent of its output into what
OL,18,Fthey describe as a vital part of the
OL,19,Feconomy.
