OL,3,CFamilies 'trying to survive instead of
OL,4,Cthrive' amid childcare crisis
OL,6,FParents have told UTV they just can't
OL,7,Fafford any further delay.
OL,9,FChristopher Eisenstadt and his wife
OL,10,FLisbeth Vermeir have spent tens of
OL,11,Fthousands of pounds paying for their
OL,12,Fson to be in full-time daycare since
OL,13,Fhe was baby.
OL,15,FHarvey is now three and in nursery and
OL,16,Fdespite reducing his hours to wrap
OL,17,Faround care, the family say the cost
OL,18,Fis crippling.
