OL,6,F"It still amounts to about #800 a
OL,7,Fmonth for the five days, so it is
OL,8,Freally, really expensive," Mr
OL,9,FEisenstadt said.
OL,11,FIn England, parents benefit from
OL,12,Fchildcare support measures which were
OL,13,Fexpanded in March last year to include
OL,14,F30 hours of free provision for
OL,15,Fchildren under 5 from September 2025.
OL,17,FIn Northern Ireland, four and five-
OL,18,Fyear-olds receive 12.5 hours of free
OL,19,Fpre-school classes but childcare is
OL,20,Fnot funded.
