OL,6,FDaycare owners say they're doing all
OL,7,Fthey can not to pass on rising costs
OL,8,Fto parents, but they're warning that
OL,9,Fwithout urgent intervention the
OL,10,Findustry could collapse.
OL,12,F"Costs are rising daily," said Ann
OL,13,FBell, a daycare provider in Kircubbin.
OL,14,F"It's spiralling, and I'm pretty sure
OL,15,Fit's the same in every nursery at the
OL,16,Fminute.
