OL,3,CFamilies 'trying to survive instead of
OL,4,Cthrive' amid childcare crisis
OL,6,FThe campaign group Melted Parents says
OL,7,Ffunding for a childcare strategy could
OL,8,Flead to a positive ripple effect
OL,9,Facross the economy.
OL,11,FA survey of thousands of parents found
OL,12,Falmost 80% have considered reducing
OL,13,Ftheir hours or giving up their careers
OL,14,Faltogether due to the soaring costs.
OL,16,F"We have had hundreds of parents
OL,17,Fcontact us to let us know how much
OL,18,Fthis crisis is affecting their
OL,19,Ffamily," said Rebecca Harper from
OL,20,FMelted Parents.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/10
