OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,7,FEducation said: "The minister has made
OL,8,Fclear his ambition for the development
OL,9,Fof an Early Learning and Childcare
OL,10,FStrategy as a top priority.
OL,12,F"He is acutely aware that the cost of
OL,13,Fchildcare puts immense strain on
OL,14,Ffamily finances and, in some cases,
OL,15,Fprevents parents from entering and
OL,16,Fremaining in the workforce.
