OL,3,CFamilies 'trying to survive instead of
OL,4,Cthrive' amid childcare crisis
OL,6,F"The minister is committed to
OL,7,Fdelivering a bespoke and affordable
OL,8,Fscheme for Northern Ireland that
OL,9,Faddresses the challenges that we face
OL,10,Fand delivers the outcomes that we want
OL,11,Fto achieve.
OL,13,F"He appreciates that putting in place
OL,14,Fthe full infrastructure required will
OL,15,Ftake time and so is also considering
OL,16,Fwhat short-term measures might be
OL,17,Fpossible to ease current pressures.
